{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"288daf9e0f","title":"武汉大学右派分子关于土地改革运动的言论","origin":"1957年9月1日《武汉大学右派言论录编》。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b613df61e9","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"288daf9e0f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5e0e2c5cb0","type":"title","text":"武汉大学右派分子关于土地改革运动的言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"288daf9e0f"},{"id":"b53124220e","type":"paragraph","text":"“土改中吊打地主都是不人道的。”","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"288daf9e0f"},{"id":"92674723a9","type":"paragraph","text":"“土改中斗争地主太残酷了。”","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"288daf9e0f"},{"id":"369cb91b44","type":"paragraph","text":"“某些地主对农民本来就好，没有什么剥削，只是一些土改干部，故意挑起来搞。又如强迫地主儿子去打地主父亲，连人偷也不要，这是什么搞法！”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"288daf9e0f"},{"id":"a2ee0793ab","type":"paragraph","text":"“什么土地改革，还不是有田就分，报上说得很好，实际上，说是一套，做的又是一套。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"288daf9e0f"},{"id":"2bea035998","type":"paragraph","text":"“土改糟得很，你们湖北还好，我们湖南更糟。”（按：这段话是右派分子对一位地主家庭出身的同学，在土改中情绪不安时说的）。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"288daf9e0f"}],"page":{"id":"5ce47ad473","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"288daf9e0f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}